This paper is about developing a learning algorithm for approximating the optimal selection of computations, which is a key aspect of artificial intelligence. The paper discusses reinforcement learning, metareasoning, and planning, which are all topics that fall under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.AI. Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (machine learning), cs.RO (robotics), cs.SY (systems and control), and cs.NE (neural and evolutionary computing), as these are all related to the topics discussed in the paper.
